  "body": "Once we have a running beacon chain node, we will want visibility into the running internals of the software. Many other client teams have been using [Prometheus](https://prometheus.io/) and [Grafana](https://grafana.com) to help with this.\r\n\r\nWe will want to add a monitoring module that exposes a prometheus metric collection endpoint and tracks relevant metrics.\r\n\r\nRelevant links:\r\n- https://github.com/ethereum/eth2.0-metrics/blob/master/metrics.md - Which beacon chain specific items should be monitored\r\n- https://github.com/siimon/prom-client - prometheus nodejs client\r\n- https://github.com/SimenB/node-prometheus-gc-stats - nodejs gc monitoring",
